official_title: Expressing the sense of Congress with respect to certain regulations of the Occupational Safety and Health Administration.

summary.text: Requests the Occupational Safety and Health Administration to publish, within one year, proposed amended regulations that specify the components of an adequate operator training program and certification system for operators of powered industrial trucks.
